::Zardus::

Zardus nods as he walks off toward the base's exit. "Contact Liono about it, 
Icedeamon. He is in controll of the Ark."

Arriving at the base's exit, he looks at the equipment Nemesis had gathered. 
"Ok. Let's go get some energon." He says, looking down at his scanner. "There 
is energon south of here." He says and flies off southward.
